Write a complete program that will take a database of video files black and white movies, and train a neural net to colorize the movies. The training set will be already existing black and white movies that have been colorized.
In addition the program will isolate the audio files of the movies and create a youtube channel and podcast that will play the audio of the movie seperate on a 24 hour stream.
In addition the program will generate from the audio files subtitles from existing databases of .srt files for the movies, and will train a machine learning program to line up the subtitles to the specific and correct times in the video
In addition the program will generate GIF from the movie in increaments of 42 frames throughout the movie and store it in a folder that is the name of the movie.
The program should included backend code, and front end code. Along with any package and dependiences that are required.
